# Strategic Planning — Timeline and Gantt Verification

- When the user asks to **check correctness of order distribution on the timeline**, **validate calculations**, or **verify Gantt / planning logic**, use the **checklist** in `.cursor/docs/TIMELINE_DISTRIBUTION_CHECKLIST.md`.
- Go through the relevant checklist sections (duration, overlaps, cross-shift splits, general), compare with the code in `backend/core/services/strategic_planning_service.py` and data/UI as needed, and report any discrepancies or confirm compliance.
- When adding or changing logic that affects planning (durations, shift boundaries, slot finding, splitting across shifts), consider updating the checklist and re-verifying affected items.
